# Optional provider-specific environment configuration.
# Agent_OS setup does not require this file.
# Preferred provider setup: run `pi`, then `/login`, then choose your provider.
#
# If you explicitly use Anthropic via environment variables, you may set:
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# Optional — defaults to ./data_store/knowledge.db (project-local)
# Set to share memory across multiple projects:
# BRAIN_DB_PATH=$HOME/.knowledge-brain/knowledge.db
